Package ru.nsu.voronova

package ru.nsu.voronova
  • Class Summary
    Class
    Description
    Diploma
    This class allows to create an analogue of the diploma received by students upon graduation from the university.
    QualifyingWork
    This record is intended to describe the qualifying work.
    RecordBook
    This class allows to create an analogue of the record book, which is issued to students upon admission to a university.
    Semester
    This class allows you to add and change information about the results of intermediate attestation for the current semester.
    Student
    This class allows specifying information about the student, including their name, surname, specialty in which they are studying and their current semester.
    Subject
    This record is intended to describe subjects.
  • Enum Class Summary
    Enum Class
    Description
    Grade
    This class identifies all types of grades that a student can receive for attestation and assigns them a certain number of points used to calculate the average score.
  • Exception Summary
    Exception
    Description
    DefectiveRecordBookException
    Thrown to indicate that a field referenced in a errorMessage parameter has been assigned an invalid value.
    IncorrectGradeFormatException
    Thrown to indicate if the grade for the semester was specified incorrectly.
    NoQualifyingWorkException
    Thrown to indicate if the qualifying work was not added to diploma.
    RecordBookException
    This class generalizes the classes of exceptions for the class RecordBook.
    SemesterNumberOutOfBoundsException
    Thrown to indicate if the number of the semester was specified as negative or too big number.
